---
import Page from "../layouts/Page.astro";

import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Page>
  <main class="min-h-dvh flex flex-col items-center px-4">
    <header class="text-center max-w-3xl mb-12 mt-16">
      <h1
        class="font-headline text-5xl text-gold-500 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider"
      >
        Legacy Wall
      </h1>
      <h2
        class="text-xl font-bold text-chrome-400 mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest"
      >
        Building Fund Program
      </h2>
      <p class="text-slate-300 text-base/7">
        The purpose of the Building Fund Program is to raise money for the
        purchase and maintenance of the CFL Motorcycle Ministry Clubhouse.
        Proceeds are dedicated specifically to the Clubhouse Building Fund to
        honor all who have contributed.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section
      class="max-w-2xl text-center p-8 border-2 border-gold-500 bg-asphalt-900 rounded-sm shadow-lg mb-20 mx-auto"
    >
      <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl text-gold-500 mb-2">
        Dedicated Supporters
      </h3>
      <p
        class="text-chrome-400 text-sm font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-tighter"
      >
        $5,000 Donation Level
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm/6 italic">
        Includes an Individual Custom Wooden Plaque with personalized engraved
        metal plaques.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="w-full max-w-6xl">
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-16 max-w-4xl w-full mx-auto"
      >
        <div
          class="p-4 border border-gold-500/30 bg-asphalt-900 text-center rounded-sm"
        >
          <div class="text-gold-500 font-bold">VIP</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">$1,000 Donation</div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="p-4 border border-chrome-400/30 bg-asphalt-900 text-center rounded-sm"
        >
          <div class="text-chrome-400 font-bold">Gold</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">$500 Donation</div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="p-4 border border-slate-400/30 bg-asphalt-900 text-center rounded-sm"
        >
          <div class="text-slate-400 font-bold">Silver</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">$300 Donation</div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="p-4 border border-orange-800/30 bg-asphalt-900 text-center rounded-sm"
        >
          <div class="text-orange-800 font-bold">Bronze</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">$100 Donation</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="w-full max-w-6xl mb-20 px-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div class="md:col-span-2">
          <div
            class="aspect-video md:aspect-auto md:h-full w-full bg-asphalt-900 border border-chrome-400/20 rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-sm"
          >
            <img
              src="/christ-for-life-legecy-wall.jpeg"
              alt="Legacy Wall Feature"
              class="size-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <div
            class="aspect-video w-full bg-asphalt-900 border border-chrome-400/20 rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-sm"
          >
            <img
              src="/christ-for-life-legecy-wall-gold.jpeg"
              alt="Legacy Wall Detail View"
              class="size-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="aspect-video w-full bg-asphalt-900 border border-chrome-400/20 rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-sm"
          >
            <img
              src="/christ-for-life-legecy-wall-vip.jpeg"
              alt="Legacy Wall Close-up"
              class="size-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="aspect-video w-full bg-asphalt-900 border border-chrome-400/20 rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-sm"
          >
            <img
              src="/christ-for-life-legacey-wall-rows.jpeg"
              alt="Legacy Wall Close-up"
              class="size-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-24 px-4">
      <div
        class="relative overflow-hidden bg-asphalt-900 border border-gold-500/20 p-8 md:p-12 text-center rounded-sm shadow-2xl"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 size-64 bg-gold-500/5 blur-3xl rounded-full"
        >
        </div>

        <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
          <h2
            class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-divine-white uppercase tracking-wider"
          >
            Leave Your <span class="text-gold-500">Legacy</span>
          </h2>

          <p class="text-slate-300 text-base/7 max-w-2xl">
            Be a permanent part of our story. By contributing to the Clubhouse
            Building Fund, your name or organization will be honored on the
            Christ For Life Legacy Wall. Contact our President today to secure
            your place.
          </p>

          <a
            href="mailto:president@christforlife.org?subject=Legacy%20Wall%20Inquiry"
            class="group flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xs bg-gold-500 px-8 py-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-asphalt-950 transition-all hover:bg-gold-50 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(212,175,55,0.3)]"
          >
            <span>Join the Wall</span>
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="size-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2.5"
                d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>

          <p
            class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-chrome-500 font-bold"
          >
            Direct Inquiry to the President
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Page>
